creator: Cleaner studio
descriptionHtml:
Deep Clean is a powerful mobile phone cleaning tool. It can help you clean up your phone's junk files in depth and improve the speed of your Android device. Including cache cleaning, garbage cleaning, CPU cooling, application manager, etc. Deep Clean is an ideal choice to clean up RAM, improve device performance and increase the speed of Android devices!

◕‿◕ One-click cleaning
The powerful mobile phone cleaner can easily clean up useless applications or residual junk files and cached files. This is the main factor that affects the performance of the phone. It can also free up storage space. Use the garbage cleaner to clean up the phone memory to increase the memory!

◕‿◕ Speed up
Forcibly close the background process and release RAM to improve the performance of the device.

◕‿◕ File management
Independently researched and developed ultra-deep management to help you manage files quickly and effectively, allowing you to easily find the files you want. With the file manager, you can delete the files you choose with one click.

◕‿◕ Picture management
Deep Clean can scan the gallery, intelligently analyze similar photos, and automatically clean up similar or duplicate photos to free up storage space.

◕‿◕ Battery information
The remaining battery size is displayed for easy management of smartphones.

◕‿◕ Wi-Fi security
Scan for unauthorized WiFi and never worry about the security of your phone.

Simple to use and easy to operate, we try to remove all unnecessary things and bring the most convenient and simple application

title: Deep Clean Booster Space Clean

creator: Cleaner studio
descriptionHtml:
Deep Clean is a powerful mobile phone cleaning tool. It can help you clean up your phone's junk files in depth and improve the speed of your Android device. Including cache cleaning, garbage cleaning, CPU cooling, application manager, etc. Deep Clean is an ideal choice to clean up RAM, improve device performance and increase the speed of Android devices!

Features：
One-click cleaning
The powerful mobile phone cleaner can easily clean up useless applications or residual junk files and cached files. This is the main factor that affects the performance of the phone. It can also free up storage space. Use the garbage cleaner to clean up the phone memory to increase the memory!

Speed up
Forcibly close the background process and release RAM to improve the performance of the device.

File management
Independently researched and developed ultra-deep management to help you manage files quickly and effectively, allowing you to easily find the files you want. With the file manager, you can delete the files you choose with one click.

Picture management
Deep Clean can scan the gallery, intelligently analyze similar photos, and automatically clean up similar or duplicate photos to free up storage space.

Super power saving
Discover all kinds of power-consuming applications hidden in the background of the system, and choose to close high-power-consuming applications according to your own needs, so as to truly extend the remaining available time of the battery. Various power saving modes are also supported.

App lock
Lock phone settings and apps as needed to prevent private information from being peeped. You can choose a numeric password or a graphic password to lock your phone.

Wi-Fi security
Scan for unauthorized WiFi and never worry about the security of your phone.

Game acceleration
Close unnecessary processes and apps to free up memory and improve your phone's performance.

Privacy browser
After exiting the program, all data and browsing history will be deleted, and no data will be saved.

Simple to use and easy to operate, we try to remove all unnecessary things and bring the most convenient and simple application!
